If you have an Apple laptop (running OSX) you already have python installed. If you have a computer running windows, you will need to install python; the best instructions I\'92ve seen for that can be found on {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://docs.python-guide.org/en/latest/starting/install/win/"}}{\fldrslt http://docs.python-guide.org/en/latest/starting/install/win/}} . Following these instructions will get you to a basic python 2.7 installation, which you may find useful in any case. \
